'''吉姆·班克斯'''（{{lang-en|Jim Banks}}，{{bd|1979年|7月16日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的政治家，黨籍[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]。自2010年開始，他擔任印第安納州參議員<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.indystar.com/story/news/politics/2014/12/08/amanda-banks-fills-husbands-senate-seat-afghanistan/20106935/ | title =Amanda Banks fills husband’s Senate seat while he’s in Afghanistan | author =Hannah Troyer | author2 =''[[Indianapolis_Star|Indianapolis Star]]'' | publisher =indystar.com | date =December 8, 2014 | accessdate =2016-11-14 | archive-date =2017-12-20 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20171220134402/https://www.indystar.com/story/news/politics/2014/12/08/amanda-banks-fills-husbands-senate-seat-afghanistan/20106935/ | dead-url =no }}</ref>。在從政之前他曾在美軍服役。2016年，他代表共和黨參選印第安納州第三選舉區聯邦眾議院議員<ref>{{cite web | url =http://www.journalgazette.net/news/local/Banks-announces-candidacy-for-Congress | title =Banks announces candidacy for Congress | publisher =journalgazette.net | author =Brian Francisco | author2 =''[[Fort_Wayne_Journal_Gazette|Fort Wayne Journal Gazette]]'' | date =May 12, 2015 | access-date =2016-11-14 | archive-date =2019-12-25 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20191225034615/https://www.journalgazette.net/news/local/Banks-announces-candidacy-for-Congress | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

